bloonix-fcgi (0.5) released at 2015-03-09

    * Improved output of server-status.

bloonix-fcgi (0.4) released at 2014-12-08

    * Ignoring "child $pid died 13".
    * New parameter max_program_size that defaults to 1GB.
    * USR1 and USR2 signals are now forwarded to all children.

bloonix-fcgi (0.3) released at 2014-11-03

    * Fixed: try to fixing malformed utf8 strings.
    * Updated the license information.

bloonix-fcgi (0.2) released at 2014-10-16

    * Improved logging for signals hup, int, term and pipe.

bloonix-fcgi (0.1) released at 2014-08-25

    * Initial release.
